CHANGES

Version 1.0.3 (2025-09-26)

- Introduced the transactional mail model and API route updates so stored templates, attachments, and message delivery flow through `api_txmail` instead of the removed `api_template` (src/models/txmail.ts, src/api/mailer.ts, src/models/db.ts).
- Let authenticated clients upload form templates via the API, aligning filename/slug generation with the new singular config structure (src/api/forms.ts, src/models/form.ts, config-example/form-template/default.njk).
- Replaced the bespoke Nunjucks loader with `@technomoron/unyuck` to flatten includes and collect referenced assets before persisting them (src/models/init.ts, package.json).
- Refreshed tooling and metadata (ESLint/Prettier configs, README, ecosystem config) to match the renamed package and repository (eslint.config.mjs, .prettierrc, README.md, ecosystem.config.cjs, package.json).
- Added workspace metadata and sample templates so pnpm and new installs pick up example assets (pnpm-workspace.yaml, config-example/tx-template/default.njk).
